[SHORT DESC]
Lowers the foe's Attack 1 stage. Decreases wild encounter rate.
[LONG DESC]
<p>Lowers the enemy's Attack 1 stage upon entering the battlefield. Affects both opponents in doubles. Activates even if gained through Trace, Skill Swap, or Role Play. When a Pok√©mon with this ability is first in the party, wild encounters have a lower chance of occurring. (Emerald only)</p>